By far, the most pathetic song of the most pathetic and musically inferior season of Coke studio. I wonder if the quality of Coke studio has been destroyed on purpose or the failure is fluky. You are better off making your pathetic crap at your basement in your home Mr. Faakhir so that we don't have to listen to your sh%t. 

This could've been done in a million different ways & million times better than what Faakhir could do.

Great Loss for listeners & a great opportunity missed by Momena due to pathetic & talent-less Faakhir. 

Faakhir should come forward & apologize to Late Khan sb , Rahat sb, Momena & Listeners of coke studio
